name:                chop$
stack:               ( -- u )
return stack:        ( -- )
string stack:        ( $1 -- $2 $3 ... $u+1 )
contexts:            stateless
category:            strings

decription:          splits top of string stack at space delimimiters into strings,
                     all of them pushed to string stack. Returned u informs of the
                     string count places on string stack.

standard:            no
                     standard has no equivalent